+        Basic usage of :meth:`flat` works similar to the pack() routines.
+
+        >>> flat(4)
+        b'\x04\x00\x00\x00'
+
+        :meth:`flat` works with strings, bytes, lists, and dictionaries.
+
+        >>> flat(b'X')
